## Consuming Branding Data

### Tailwind Config

```typescript
// tailwind.config.js
import colors from '../../branding/colors.json';
import typography from '../../branding/typography.json';

export default {
  theme: {
    colors: {
      primary: colors.primary,
      secondary: colors.secondary,
      foreground: colors.foreground,
      background: colors.background,
      destructive: colors.destructive,
    },
    fontFamily: {
      heading: [typography.heading.family, 'sans-serif'],
      body: [typography.body.family, 'sans-serif'],
    },
  },
};
```

### CSS Variables

```css
:root {
  --color-primary: #F4B4C0;
  --color-secondary: #A7D1AB;
  --font-heading: 'Nunito Sans', sans-serif;
  --font-body: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
}
```

### Percepta Theming

Percepta loads branding JSON directly into its theming system.

### React Native

```typescript
import colors from '../../branding/colors.json';

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  button: {
    backgroundColor: colors.primary,
  },
});
```

## Branding Flow

```
branding/ (meta layer)
    ↓
projects/wegoby-portfolio/ (implements via tailwind)
    ↓
projects/percepta/ (theming system)
    ↓
miniapps/{app}/ (can override via theme.json)
```

